R01D=<body></font><font size="5"><b>When Playing with the Oztea 1941 Mod you will have to Edit 10 Damage to the London Factory and 3 Each to the Harbor and Airbase.<br><br>The Malta Airbase will also Require 5 Damage as well as the Southern Italy Harbor.<br><br>The Bismark in 118 Sea Zone and the Italian Battleship in 97 Sea Zone will need to be damaged.</b></body>
